data.title: Shopping Events
data.meta_description: Shop 'til you drop at these exclusive multi-designer shopping events and destinations in Second Life.
data.text:
FLF Birthday Bash

Fifty Linden Fridays invites you to their birthday bash, celebrating 15 years in Second Life! The event will feature 100+ designers with brand new items all for L$50 each, plus a free gift at each booth. The event runs from August 23rd to September 13th.

Uber

Uber is a monthly shopping event featuring unique creations from talented designers in Second Life. It opens on the 25th of each month. Learn more at https://ubersecondlife.wixsite.com/home

The Fifty

The Fifty is a luxe, highly curated monthly shopping experience in one dedicated location from the creators of Fifty Linden Fridays & FLF Events. The event opens at noon on the 25th of each month. For more info, visit linktr.ee/thefiftysl

Cosmopolitan Events

Cosmopolitan Events is home of the Hello Tuesday weekly discount event and Cosmopolitan bi-weekly event. Find anything you need for your Second life living at one place. There's always something new to find from SL most quality designers! Come by and enjoy shopping at Cosmopolitan!

Manhood Event

Manhood is a themed monthly shopping event that opens on the 25th of each month at 1pm PT. It brings together a variety of talented Second Life creators, offering a wide range of products and services specially designed for male avatars. From high-quality clothing and accessories to innovative gadgets and stylish home decor items, Manhood is the ideal destination for men looking to enhance their appearance and virtual lifestyle. Learn more at manhoodsl.com

Velour Mall

Velour Mall caters to all your avatar needs with a variety of high-end stores that sell skins, shoes, cosmetics, poses, accessories, and more! Some of the stores include Velour Beauty, It Girls, Faenzo Hair, Salvadori Paris, and more.

Abnormality

Abnormality is a shopping event focused on all things human-alternative and furry, running every 3 months from the 7th to the 28th! All are welcome to come and enjoy the shopping to find something new or enjoy the scenery of each round's themed decoration. This month's theme is Badlands! Learn more at abnormality.is

Collabor88

Collabor88 is a fashion forward destination, where the most well-loved content creators in Second Life get together to bring shoppers a superb selection of well-crafted merchandise at affordable prices. Collabor88 opens on the 8th of every month with a different theme.

eBody Reborn Event

eBody's Reborn Event is a monthly shopping event where you can find clothing, shoes, accessories, shapes, skins, tattoos, etc; all fitted for the Reborn body. The event begins on the 22nd at noon each month and ends on the 5th of the following month. For more information, visit abarebody.blogspot.com

Dubai Event

Dubai is a monthly shopping event that starts on the 20th of each month with 110 designers per round, offering exclusive content of the highest quality. The build is a modern, diaphanous eclectic style, with architectural references to the Arab style in a minimalist way.

ACCESS Event

ACCESS Event is a monthly shopping event starting on 12th of each month, ending on 8th of the next. There is no theme and no limits. You will see many well-known, established, and favorite designers together with fresh new content from the many extremely talented creators. ACCESS designers will give their best to bring you unique and original creations to support the best shopping experience.

Kustom9

Kustom9 is a recurring fashion event which opens on the 15th of each month. Come and explore the exclusive creations of over 50 designers in Second Life.

Man Cave

Man Cave caters to the modern man with exclusive monthly items/releases that promise to entertain, stimulate your mind and keep you looking your best! With everything from cars, gear, rides and style, Man Cave has the best that Second Life has to offer. Man Cave starts on the 17th of each month.

Equal10

Equal10 is a vibrant, monthly shopping event that features various items created by some of Second LifeÂ´s most popular designers and talented newcomers. This original, energetic location has something for everyone trying to get their groove on and party, with a theme of synthwave ambience. The recurring event starts on the 10th of every month with new designs. More info at equal10event.com

MENSELECTED Event

MENSELECTED Event is a monthly shopping event showcasing some of the best men's and unisex designers in Second Life since 2018. The event is open every 3rd - 26th of the month.

The Sales Room

The Sales Room is a monthly shopping event open from the 10th - 28th where some of the best Second Life designers offer their products at a discounted price of L$50 to L$99 in an event setting.

TMD - The Mens Dept

TMD is a monthly event catering to unisex/male fashion and accessories, as well as home decor. Designers place items that are priced and discounted from L$100 â L$300. The event starts at 12pm PT on the 5th of every month and ends on the last day of the month.

French Touch Event

The French Touch is a monthly shopping event open each month from the 7th through the last day of the month. It is a collective of francophone designers offering exclusive items for only L$60 and many gifts.

Update Tease Up Event

Update Tease Up is a monthly shopping event where the spotlight is on the latest bodies, cutting-edge tech, and creative addons! It is open from the 13th to the 31st of each month. Learn more at teaseupsl.wordpress.com

The Fantasy Room

Established 2013, The Fantasy Room is a monthly shopping fair dedicated to all the things fantasy! The event is open from the 1st to the 20th of each month. Learn more at synergyshoppers.wordpress.com

Anthem

Anthem is a monthly event featuring over 60 of Second Life's talented creators. The event starts on the 3rd of each month and will bring a mix of home decor, male and female clothing, skin, hair, and accessories!

Posh Event

Posh Event is a collaboration of designers that bring the most up-to-date items, including clothing, furniture, shapes, skins, animations, and more! It is a monthly event that runs from the 1st to the 17th of each month.

Sense Event

The Sense Event is a monthly event that begins on the 15th of each month. The event is focused on chic/casual-glam, but also follows seasonal trends. It showcases distinguished Second Life brands releasing content for men and women, as well as home and garden.

Swank Events

Swank is a monthly shopping event focused on providing Residents with the hottest products in home and garden, beauty, fashion, meshes and more! Everyone is more than welcome to explore and discover wonderful designs from over 100 skilled designers found at this location. New themes for the event are released on the 7th of every month.

Wanderlust Weekend

Wanderlust Weekend is a magically conjured âweekend saleâ in collaboration with Second Lifeâs most talented. Every weekend you will find specially priced items from 25 rotated Creators. The sale lasts from the strike of midnight Saturday till Sunday at midnight. Then the sale turns into a pumpkin until the following weekend! Come grab your HUD from the Magical HUD Dispenser to get started.

POSEvent

POSEvent is a monthly shopping event that opens on the 27th of each month and closes on the 19th of the next month. It has everything you need for your photography needs including poses, animations, backdrops, environment settings, and more!

Anthology

Anthology is a monthly shopping event featuring brand-new exclusive items from permanent and guest creators in a beautiful venue. It opens at 12pm PT on the 19th of each month and ends on the 17th of the next month. Learn more at linktr.ee/anthology_sl

The Darkness Event

The Darkness is a monthly shopping event where you can find any and all dark styles including Gothic, glam rock, punk, emo, urban and more. Everything is dark! The event begins at 1pm PT on the 5th of each month and closes on the 26th. Learn more at linktr.ee/thedarknessevent

LEVEL EVENT

The LEVEL event is a monthly shopping event with the purpose of bringing together some of the best designers from around the grid. The event opens at 2pm PT on the 1st of each month and closes on the 25th. Learn more at levelsl.com

ALPHA Event

ALPHA Event is a premier Second Life monthly shopping event for men. Featuring the best creators and designers bringing you a variety of men's clothing, decor, skins, hair, transportation, and lots more. In short, ALPHA is your one-stop resource for the latest in men's items under one roof. Stay ahead of the pack. The event opens on the 22nd of each month and closes on the 17th of the next month. For more info, visit access-sl.com/alpha

FaMESHed

FaMESHed is a monthly shopping event meant to showcase the best designers in Second Life. Home to 100% original mesh creators. FaMESHed opens on the 1st of each month at midday SLT (12pm SLT) until the 27th.

Planet29

Planet29 is a themed monthly shopping event focusing on Cyberpunk, Steampunk, Stars, DeepSpace, and Fantasy. It opens on the 29th of each month. Planet29 also has a $L2900 x 9 giveaway on Planet29's FB page every month, make sure to check that out facebook.com/Planet29.event

The Outlet

Seraphim brings you The Outlet Infinity Event! It is a brand new shopping experience. It never closes! Your favorite designers are bringing you previous releases at a HUGE discounted price, and changing the items weekly making sure you always get a great bargain. It's a great way to save money and update your wardrobe. See you there!

The Warehouse Sale Event

The Warehouse Sale Event is a post-apocalyptic themed region. This is a monthly shopping event that opens on the 23rd. of each month and closes on the 18th of the next month. Designers will offer 1 color or item of their choice at 10-50% discount price and Sponsors may in addition offer old releases at a price of L$150 only for the duration of the event. For more information, visit: thewarehousesale.net

Tres Chic

The Tres Chic Event is all about you! The fashion event, where the exclusive original creations of over 90 designers in Second Life are available for you to shop at your leisure from the 19th of each month until the 10th of the following month. Itâs all about You! Be Unique, Be Stylish! Be yourself, Be TrÃ¨s Chic!

We Love Role-Play

We Love Role-Play is the original and largest monthly sales-event for role-players. Here, you can buy premium items of high quality at a very nice discount, meet like-minded role-players, and find out about great new regions! The event opens at 12pm PT on the 4th of each month and closes on the 28th. More info at weloveroleplay.weebly.com

Inithium Visual Show Room

The Inithium Visual Show Room is a monthly shopping event that starts on the 19th of each month and ends on the 14th of the next month. It is officially sponsored by Inithium, and has numerous creators selling items created for the Kupra, Kups, and Kario bodies. For more information, visit inithium.com

Fable 9 - Once Upon A Time

Evil Bunny Productions presents Fable 9 - Once Upon A Time, create your own story! What is your fairy tale or horror story? Fairies, elves, fantasy, horror - the choice is yours! It is your story to write. There are Exclusives and L$10 specials! The event runs from August 3rd to 31st. Details at www.evilbunnysl.com

Autumn Is Coming Event 2024

Autumn is Coming 2024 is a shopping and treasure hunt event with over 40 participating merchants. Here you can find anything autumn-related, from accessories to decorations and outfits. There are even 13 Dinkie stores participating. It will run from 23rd August through 23rd September.

The Belleza Event

The Belleza Event is a shopping event dedicated to the Gen.X and Jake bodies by Belleza. It is a bi-monthly event that runs from the 11th to the 10th every January, March, May, July, September, and November.

BOSL Innovation Pavillion

BOSL Innovation Pavillion is home to the Best of Second Life Magazine brand which promotes all things fashion-related. Find some of the best designers, models, magazines, pageants, art shows, and more! You can also visit the winery, cafe, gardens, and the Art Gallery which showcases some of the best artists in Second Life.

Kawaii Project

The Kawaii Project is a monthly shopping event that will meet all your Kawaii needs! The event opens at 6pm PT on the 18th of each month and closes on the 12th of the next month. Learn more at fb.com/KawaiiProjectsl

Blue SL Event

The Blue SL Event is a monthly shopping event with exclusives and sale items. The event opens on the 16th of each month and closes on the 8th of the next month. Learn more at www.blueslevent.com

DisturbeD Event

DisturbeD is an edgy monthly shopping event and home for the weird and unusual. The event is open from the 8th to the 29th of each month. Learn more at disturbedslevent.wixsite.com/disturbed

FLOURISH Event

FLOURISH is not just a monthly shopping event; it's a whole vibe! Every month on the 7th, bringing you creativity from the best brands. Including apparel for both guys and gals, accessories because life's too short for boring details, add-ons to level up your avatar game, food and beverages to satisfy your virtual cravings, poses and animations to strut, dance, werk, and home and garden items to spruce up your virtual abode. Comon, let's FLOURISH! See you there! Learn more at flourisheventsl.com

Enchantment Presents Talez

Enchantment Presents Talez, a classic fairy tales remixed for contemporary and urban life shopping event and free hunt. Dive into a vibrant marketplace brimming with enchanted goods, from magical attire to mystical artifacts, all inspired by modern-day interpretations of beloved fairytales. Embark on the grid-wide hunt and uncover hidden themed treasures. The event runs from August 9th to September 1st.
